data.description: Now available in N. Lancaster! Adorable home on a spacious corner lot! If privacy is what you are looking for, this 3-bedroom 2-bath home is it! Featuring a split bedroom floor plan, open concept living with a large eat-in kitchen open to the spacious living room with bay window for tons of natural light. Enjoy a huge primary bedroom with oversize bath. Nice size secondary bedrooms with ample closet space. Enjoy relaxing on the large back porch which is covered and enclosed with wrap around windows. Conveniently located, situated just 30 minutes from Monroe and a quick drive to Lancaster, Indian Land, Rock Hill, Charlotte and Columbia for shopping, dining and travel from the Charlotte Douglas Airport.
